CustomField.label: Add continuous integration event count
CustomField.description: The number of times that the add continuous integration job event has happened. Each of these events correlates to somebody creating a new job. This can be higher than the number of currently configured jobs if the user later deleted some of the jobs
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The number of times that the add continuous integration job event has happened. Each of these events correlates to somebody creating a new job. This can be higher than the number of currently configured jobs if the user later deleted some of the jobs
